therian.operator.copy

Annotation Type PropertyCopier.Matching


  • @Documented
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public static @interface PropertyCopier.Matching
    Configures a PropertyCopier subclass for property matching.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String[] exclude
      Property names to exclude from matching.
      String[] value
      Property names to match.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract String[] value
        Property names to match. An empty array implies all matching properties that are readable on the source and writable on the target.
        Default:
        {}

      • exclude

        public abstract String[] exclude
        Property names to exclude from matching.
        Default:
        {}
